input_str: Before I started rock climbing, my life was all about whitewater. Three days after I bought my first used car (Beauty), I packed up and headed out west to Canmore, AB to a good paying raft guiding job and new rivers and creeks to kayak! Unfortunately, AB tourism was hit hard that year and trips were WAY down: instead of working 6 days a week I was lucky to do 1.
